# Figure 1 — M_BH vs. M★ for dwarf broad-line AGN
Black dashed line: Reines & Volonteri (2015) AGN relation
log(M_BH/M☉) = 7.45 + 1.05 × (log M★ − 11)
Red points: 12 broad-line dwarf AGN with measured black hole masses (from Reines & Volonteri 2015, Table 3)
Error bars: 0.5 dex (standard virial mass uncertainty)

